<% provide(:title, "Job Resources : Federal Employment") %>
<div id="content" class="interior">
  <a href="#content" class="sr-only">Content starts here.</a>


  <div class="splash">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 columns">
        <ul class="breadcrumbs" role="menubar" aria-label="Primary">
          <li class="parent"><%= link_to "Veterans Employment Center", root_path %></li>
          <li class="parent"><%= link_to "For Job Seekers", for_job_seekers_path %></li>
          <li class="parent"><%= link_to "Job Resources", job_resources_path %></li>
          <li class="active">Federal Employment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section one">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 medium-12 columns">
        <h4>Federal Hiring Process</h4>
        <div class="feature">
          <p>The federal government’s hiring process is very different from the private sector's hiring process. When applying for federal jobs, Veterans may be eligible to take advantage of hiring preferences and secure employment more quickly.</p>
          See also: <a href="http://www.fedshirevets.gov/job/filled/index.aspx" target="_blank" class="external_resource" >Federal Hiring Process</a>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <h4>How Federal Jobs are Filled</h4>
        <div class="feature">
          <p>Many Federal agencies fill their jobs like private industry by allowing applicants to contact the agency directly for additional job information and in understanding the application process.</p>
          See also: <a href="https://fedshirevets.gov/job/filled/index.aspx" target="_blank" class="external_resource" >How Federal Jobs are Filled<%= image_tag "new_window.gif", class: "external", alt: "Opens in a new window." %></a>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <h4>Work for <abbr>VA</abbr></h4>
        <div class="feature">
          <p>Why <abbr>VA</abbr>? As a Veteran, you understand the perspectives of the Veterans who have earned the benefits and health services that <abbr>VA</abbr> provides.</p>
          See also: <a href="http://vaforvets.va.gov/" target="_blank" class="external_resource" >Work for <abbr>VA</abbr></a>
        </div>

        <hr>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- Navigation -->

  <div class="navigation">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 columns">
        <h3>Related Info:</h3>
        <ul class="small-block-grid-1 medium-block-grid-3 cards small">
          <li>
            <%= link_to for_job_seekers_path do %>
              <h5>Are you a Veteran job seeker?</h5>
              <span>Visit the Job Seeker Section to search jobs, translate your skills, and build a résumé.</span>
            <% end %>
          </li>
          <li>
            <%= link_to career_fairs_path do %>
              <h5>Career Fairs</h5>
              <span>In-person and online events where Veterans, Servicemembers, and their families can meet employers and learn about job opportunities.</span>
            <% end %>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
